headline: Intercontinental Exchange (ICE) Fell Due to Investors’ Bias Toward AI Stocks
summary: Sands Capital, an investment management company, released its “Sands Capital Select Growth Strategy” Q3 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. U.S. large-cap growth equities continued to recover from a sharp sell-off in early April.
